{"tid":2489643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"性感女偶像爆私生活亂！同時陪睡熟男與鮮肉　粉怒喊：退團","createTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T05:26:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"601885cf9d66af182c7f488be422ddcd23521d73","tid":2489643,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"日本人氣女團AKB48近期不少成員出狀況，近日又有團員出事被逮著，這次是20歲成員鈴木優香，她僅出道不到2年憑藉魔鬼身材及大膽言行迅速走紅。不過昨（14日）被日媒《週刊文春》踢爆私生活頗受爭議，首先是與40多歲的製作人半同居外，卻同時被拍到與一位有傑尼斯帥氣外型的小鮮肉赴酒店開房間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111556-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111556-PH.jpg&h=37c2e87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼AKB48成員鈴木優香相當受注目。（圖／翻攝自鈴木優香IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111554-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111554-PH.jpg&h=6fae51bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被譽為日本寫真界新星的鈴木優香，近日遭日媒直擊與一40多歲男子關係互動頗為密切，4月初整整一禮拜的時間，該男大半時間都在鈴木優香家中過夜。而男子身分也被起底，正是先前鈴木優香所屬地下偶像女團「81 moment」製作人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111567-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111567-PH.jpg&h=81d2e54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鈴木優香被抓到與40多歲製作人半同居。（圖／翻攝自鈴木優香IG）<br />\n<br />\n不過最讓人傻眼的是，鈴木優香與製作人似乎是「各玩各」的狀態。上個月底鈴木優香被發現與一位帥氣小鮮肉赴池袋酒店開房間，然而男製作人也非省油的燈，4月8號也和另一位擁有偶像外型女子於酒店過夜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bunshun_online?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1382474195402072065%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F925533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbunshun_online%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1382474195402072065%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.setn.com%252Fnews%252F925533&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=0682a106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bunshun_online?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1382474195402072065%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F925533</a><br />\n<br />\n周刊問到鈴木優香，他打死不認與製作人同居，反而製作人大方坦承兩人同居中，至於自己與另一女子到酒店，則只是進行單純談話的關係。消息一出遭到撻伐，要求她退出偶像團體AKB48。"},{"pid":"682908ac689fab6879f66b31a5fa5fc44c758ac5","tid":2489643,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"拍av...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593bfb2f87017b42e34ed61cd0cfc9591ee59461","tid":2489643,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"臭婆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758839b03933c6b209a9ae0256e7dfd684a3643b","tid":2489643,"uid":366457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"推到佢下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020a3b04073e2857eb16a5859ceb9e919bd12a5b","tid":2489643,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"同宇垣美里撞樣 依種格好撚好屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f7436e33cc3a38823cc94464de1f62413390ac","tid":2489643,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"593bfb2f87017b42e34ed61cd0cfc9591ee59461","tid":2489643,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"臭婆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" cl